   Roecklein J 1987 pp 29 [USE]
   Duke J 1975 pp 6 [PH, RAIN, TEMP]
   Hartmann T 1981 pp 561 [USE]
   Small E 1994 (pers. comm.)
   Rice R 1990 pp 301-302 [FER, TEXT]
   Siemonsma J 1993 pp 280 [USE, TEMP, TEXT]

